comments.content: This pathway is a meta-pathway that represents an updated version of the Adverse Outcome Pathway 276: Inhibition of complex I of the electron transport chain leading to chemical induced Fanconi syndrome (https://aopwiki.org/aops/276). All Key Events are present as Key Event nodes, with their corresponding molecular pathways as pathway nodes.
